31
00:01:06.640 --> 00:01:07.640
And then secondly,

32
00:01:07.640 --> 00:01:09.560
because we are using DirectX 12

33
00:01:09.560 --> 00:01:12.180
and we have those higher quality reflections,

34
00:01:12.180 --> 00:01:13.520
you'll see that we start to see them

35
00:01:13.520 --> 00:01:15.960
within the actual reflections of the vehicle.

36
00:01:15.960 --> 00:01:18.600
And of course, any object that has anything

37
00:01:18.600 --> 00:01:22.600
