38
00:01:22.600 --> 00:01:26.040
So again, no lights per se within our scene right now,

39
00:01:26.040 --> 00:01:27.600
outside of just our skylight,

40
00:01:27.600 --> 00:01:30.120
but rather just the emissive material

41
00:01:30.120 --> 00:01:32.520
from this particular panel.

42
00:01:32.520 --> 00:01:33.600
So with that being said,

43
00:01:33.600 --> 00:01:36.360
